Southern Cross Group :: Investors :: Investors












 



















Southern Cross Group has built long-term relationships with our Limited Partners, the majority having invested with us since our founding in 1998.











SINCE 1998, SOUTHERN CROSS HAS BUILT A STRONG AND STABLE INVESTOR BASE, WHICH INCLUDES INDIVIDUAL AND INSTITUTIONAL INVESTORS, BOTH REGIONAL AND GLOBAL. 


Throughout our history, Southern Cross has built a strong and stable investor base. Limited 
                    Partners include well-respected local industrial groups and pension funds as well as leading 
                    global endowments, foundations and sovereign wealth funds. We have nearly 140 Limited 
                    Partners, most of them investing with us for over a decade.
From the $2.9 billion of aggregate commitments, 2% come from our professionals, evidencing that our investment proffesionals have confidence in our investment criteria and potential to generate returns. 












