Southern Cross Latin America Private Equity Fund IV, L.P.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 4:51 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Southern Cross Latin America Private Equity Fund IV, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Southern Cross Latin America Private Equity Fund IV, L.P. specializes in middle market, expansion and buyout investments in medium and large companies. It invests in all sectors. It seeks to invest in companies operating in Latin America with focus on Brazil, Chile, and Mexico. It invests between $50 million to $500 million in companies with an enterprise value between $50 million and $300 million acquiring controlling or majority stakes. The fund is set to operate for a period of ten years.


41 West Putnam Avenue2nd FloorGreenwich, CT 06830United StatesFounded in 2010



Phone: 203-629-8272

Fax: 203-629-8370








